  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Choke</em></p>\n<p>You make a crushing gesture at a creature within range. The target must make a Constitution saving throw. On a failed save target takes [[/r 10d8]] force damage and is paralyzed until the end of your next turn. On a successful save, the target takes half as much damage and is not paralyzed.</p>\n<p>You can use a bonus action while the target is paralyzed to move the target up to 10 feet in any direction.</p>\n<p><strong><em>Force Potency.</em></strong> When you cast this power using a force slot of 7th level or higher, the damage increases by [[/r 1d8]] for each slot level above 6th.</p>",
